Easiness-time-cognitive level plot.

This function computes a graph displaying the guessers plot for each quiz.

plot_etl(quiz_object, challengeLevel)

Arguments

challengeLevel

file of challengue level
df_quizzes

dataframe in long format of all quizzes (Generated with read_lc)

Value

The ETL plot

Examples

file_to_read <- "../../datasets/Dataset1/Quiz3_session12098.csv"
file_cognitivelevel <- "../../datasets/Quiz2013-14_cognitive level_HB.csv"
